overview:
CJTGolfShop.com offers the best priced golf equipment and golf gear for all ages, from top brands, as well as golf instruction, custom club fitting, club repair and a trade-In program.

Owned and managed by PGA professionals with more than 40 years experience in the golf business provides best-in-the-industry golf equipment and golf gear for men, women, seniors, and children across the U.S. We carry a huge selection of clubs, balls, bags, shoes, gloves and more all from top brands including Adidas, Adam, Callaway, Cobra, Mizuno, Nike, Ping, Puma, Taylor Made, Titleist, and more. All products shipped directly from manufacturer under warranty. We also offer professional golf instruction, custom club fitting, and club repair. Our signature Golf Equipment Trade-In Program let’s you upgrade to our newest brands and products using a simple credit program. Simply create your account, become a member and get the best deal in golf. Shop online at www.cjtgolfshop.com or call toll-free 888-PRO-4CJT.
